summary: Hello, I am Marieke, I grew up in the Netherlands and in recent years I have lived and worked in several countries and followed various courses. This resulted in a strong vision for the future that I want to continue to work for! Do you see similarities in the experiences, education and skills below or a good partner, please contact me and maybe it can be the start of a collaboration.
